title: Compiled model: An item with the same key has already been added
body:
### Repro

Note this is a regression from .NET 8.

1. Clone https://github.com/GZTimeWalker/GZCTF
2. Change the TFM to net9.0
3. Update all efcore packages to the latest nightly version
4. Change the line `internal static readonly JsonSerializerOptions JsonOptions = new() { WriteIndented = false };` in `src/GZCTF/Models/AppDbContext.cs:14` to make it `public` so that it won't hit the exception where efcore hasn't implemented the support for private static field access
5. `cd src/GZCTF`
6. `dotnet ef dbcontext optimize -c AppDbContext -o Models/Data/Compiled --verbose`
